description: GILDERS PASTE-Baroque Art Gilders Paste. Let the glowing metallic or vivid jewel-like tones of these innovative, decorative, non- tarnishing pastes transform picture frames, furniture, metalwork, artwork, molding, ceramics, textiles or almost any clean dry surface. This paste is made of highly concentrated metallic and organic pigments blended with a wax base. Can be used indoors or outdoors. This package contains one 1.5oz tin of paste. Available in a variety of designs, each sold separately. Conforms to ASTM D 4236. Made in USA.
